Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:07.77,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reliable friend who can \Nprotect you in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:08.98,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.99,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ganba Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.88,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,How could I lose my sight \Nat such a crucial moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.21,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.24,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.68,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We still have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.10,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.23,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to release our power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:14.48,Default,Banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congratulations On Your Win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:14.48,Default,Banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirahamazaka High's \NTanaka Taichi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.40,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:18.07,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that holds all of our hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.11,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The nationals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.95,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The Eternal Holy Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:27.83,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Turn courage and tears into strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.07,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.45,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.66,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I've imagined being here a million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:34.84,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Now face your colossal foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.92,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.16,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to stand on a grand stage someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.21,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You mean for archery?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:42.55,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Forever! (Forever!) Forever! (Forever!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:36.76,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:37.79,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's horses for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.17,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.55,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be a jockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.88,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to race to the finish ahead of the pack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a horse running at breakneck speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.40,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.31,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.50,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Put a sock in it, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.54,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not time for congratulations yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.82,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is only the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.31,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to put you in \Na champion's frame of mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:04.91,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.33,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Darn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to waste Wien's efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.75,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your uppity attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.36,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cheer him on together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:23.59,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you maracas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:33.44,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now face your colossal foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.24,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.57,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not feeling very well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.82,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:55.54,Default,Titl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 5 \NThrowing Away and Holding On
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we were being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.76,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You do tend to go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:06.13,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you start playing badmin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.04,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shorten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.77,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Would Shirahamazaka High School's Tanaka Taichi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kindly proceed to his designated court.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,To arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.39,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.88,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:21.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a battle cry used during peasant \Nuprisings in the Edo period.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.55,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Willing to sacrifice their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd pour a nutritious\Ndrink into a sake cup and—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Konatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.41,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.62,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.50,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.67,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.12,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.21,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have this in pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.47,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.72,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we only have what's on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.83,Default,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Red would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.04,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.96,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.89,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.03,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.53,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.76,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.34,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Beg your pardon, but could I get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.11,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.18,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.37,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The register is right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.10,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirahamazaka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.10,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Match won by Wada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Being in the top eight is pretty amazing, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.08,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:51.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He needed to place in the top \Nfour to go to the championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.24,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, he was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun's taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.87,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me a green tea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.55,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hold my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.08,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.56,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.65,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I was just doing some visualization training,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while it's all still fresh in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.11,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.87,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.82,Default,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,How long has Tanaka-kun \Nbeen playing badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.75,Default,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Since around third grade, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:46.27,Default,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted his own racquet the \Nsecond I joined the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.45,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you've been playing since grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you go to a high school \Nwith a badminton program?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.46,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.36,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I could ride my bike to Shira High and,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the time, the club had more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:05.82,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There was also a player I really admired...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So that player's the reason \Nyou took up badmin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.24,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop oversimplifying things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.64,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:17.87,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, that's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.23,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,They sell hot ones even in the summer, \Nso you don't catch a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.98,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.59,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Wakana's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She has seemed a bit down lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.19,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,The water's super cold, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.10,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.24,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,It is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.12,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Okita...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.51,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.55,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Had my first spill in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.30,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.43,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But let's keep this a secret from Sawa, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.13,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,She'll just say I'm getting \Ntoo old for this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.04,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Spunkier every year, I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.51,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You seem quite close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.07,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Boy is it hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.10,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you can put it down anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.96,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You must be drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.19,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.74,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.25,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.50,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.29,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.98,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.05,Default,box,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Schoo \NAlbu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.05,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.54,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:57.18,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to be an alumni \Nof Shira High, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.34,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Shira High or Kama High
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were the only choices for schools around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.49,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:08.70,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this your mother, Mahiru-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:15.53,Default,Banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congratulations On Your Victory, Choir Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.59,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.59,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.53,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,She was one year ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.02,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here's Takakura-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:21.60,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Takakura Naoko the vice principal now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:27.40,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a nice copy of that, \Nso come pick it up sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.38,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.38,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Were you all in choir together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.77,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.20,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,They took that photo after we won \Nthe national competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother never told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.87,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wasn't told about her illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.28,Default,Old2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because she was in the midst of entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.23,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.24,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Excuse me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.49,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.91,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:12.74,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, want me to make dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.13,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.76,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Slow day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.55,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.23,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.68,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so scared when \Nthey told me you collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.90,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you'll be discharged soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to get a cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.91,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to take better \Ncare of yourself, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet writing a song with \Nyou would perk me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:51.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You could tell me your ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and what you think about—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.03,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.47,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exams are coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then why don't we sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.97,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not in the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:12.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't be able to put in your \Nbest effort if you're so grumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.52,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now you're mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.30,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she would've gotten better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if we'd written a song together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.34,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you stop fooling around and teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.19,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not {\i1}Chorübungen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:44.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we sang together like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.18,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Studying is very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but music will still be there long after exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:58.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope music will always be your companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so never forget how much you lov—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.49,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.33,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of that matters \Nif I don't pass my exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.59,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Strained back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.04,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.26,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you do Saturday and Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.64,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, we have to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.27,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.75,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:37.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.19,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Mr. Touno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.91,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's his back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.18,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of helping him \Nin the fields next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:46.87,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hidehiko-san has an office job, \Nso he can't suddenly take time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take two or three days. \NThat okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.21,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.21,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll get sushi delivered for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.45,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.20,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.69,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about \Ngetting rid of the piano in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.86,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I use it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if someone with a \Npassion for music could have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.67,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what Mom would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.53,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.67,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I only need a little player for my CD's,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could get rid of all my extra stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use the space for a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.91,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.42,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some calls tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:56.54,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,The Kanto region will see \Ncloud cover this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong low pressure system is currently
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.22,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,moving north from the Ogasawara Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that from around noon to evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,weather conditions will deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.27,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if your classes are going to run late,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should probably take a raincoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.60,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's supposed to pick up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.57,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.55,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming to take the piano today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.03,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.59,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I labeled everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:34.65,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.48,Default,boxes,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Junk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.16,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:54.60,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.41,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:56.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.91,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a goldfish! A goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.98,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.19,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.75,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.77,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:08.17,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay then, we'll compromise \Nand say he's a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.68,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does the dolphin sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.33,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.46,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading out at 3:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.08,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you need me for anything, call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.39,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have the \Ngreatest reception out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you know Touno's number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.95,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can order sushi for dinner, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.82,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.64,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Want to head to club practice together later?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating Taichi \Nplacing in the top eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.06,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to do some shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can get home before the rain starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating the \Nbadminton competition now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka's treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.37,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm kind of busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I got cake for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,A gigantic strawberry one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.66,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you eat it before you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.70,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.62,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.11,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Something's definitely up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.10,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she doesn't like strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.50,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.48,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I annoy her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That might be closer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.91,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.55,Default,enve,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Food Money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.41,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.58,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:37.26,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.44,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.22,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.36,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you to put my raincoat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, I'll get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.08,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.07,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should prepare your things yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have the test schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:11.95,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not forgetting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.92,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.34,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.36,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Dora?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.61,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.62,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.85,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go back inside before you're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:12.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to walk with my daughter, Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:18.73,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In times of sickness and times of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In happy times and sad times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:29.02,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I truly believe I can write \Na song like that with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:35.50,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me, a song is a way to express love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:42.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Wakana has taught me \Nso many important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could put all my feelings for her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}into a song, and then sing that song with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:57.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could hear Wakana's song,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would be absolutely complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:24.12,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't say, "I'm leaving."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:26.97,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.36,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.88,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll never sing together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:50.28,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.02,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:30.08,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, what do you \Nthink we need most?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:33.99,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 6\NLaughing and Remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:30.80,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.02,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wakana, are you free now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
